    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Essentially a longer version of a scimitar, but with a thinner blade, the elven curve blade is exceptionally rare.</em></p>\n<p>You receive a +2 circumstance bonus to your Combat Maneuver Defense whenever a foe attempts to sunder your elven curve blade due to its flexible metal.</p>\n<p>You can use the @Compendium[pf1.feats.vWiTqHC4Y3Xn1Pme]{Weapon Finesse}&nbsp;feat to apply your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;modifier instead of your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Strength</a>&nbsp;modifier to attack rolls with an elven curve blade sized for you, even though it isn&rsquo;t a light weapon.</p>",
